{"tid":2272584,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南丫海難8年　疏忽無人被控　3犯錯照升職　最高級至助理處長","createTime":"2020-11-05T06:50:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T15:30:29.000Z","uid":261647,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"11d30225de2aa927379bb72f93c429e6807a1196","tid":2272584,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T06:50:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/3616557778429816/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fphotos%2Fa.720050934747196%2F3616557778429816%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=GnUrxgUttZjT4wJVsekm4CWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=9c8babfa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/3616557778429816/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n2012 年的南丫海難 39 人命喪大海，他們乘坐的「南丫四號」被揭批圖、驗船錯漏百出，港府亦指海事處 17 人涉行為不當。不過調查 8 年後，警方、律政司終於本周二（3 日）指證據不足，不會對其他人作檢控。<br />\n<br />\n《立場新聞》調查發現，9 名在獨立調查中被點名裁斷犯錯的海事處人員中，3 人竟獲晉升，其中一人在 7 年間升兩級至助理處長，其職責更包括管轄海事意外調查部門，月薪近 18 萬元。<br />\n<br />\n記者分別向運輸及房屋局，以及公務員事務局查詢，該 3 人曾否就「南丫四號」工作被處分、為何被裁定犯錯仍獲晉升，兩政策局未正面回應。<br />\n<br />\n有罹難者家屬指，對涉事人員竟獲晉升感錯愕及悲憤，認為對死者及家屬極之不公道。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/E58D97E4B8ABE6B5B7E99BA3-01_AAiUm_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FE58D97E4B8ABE6B5B7E99BA3-01_AAiUm_1200x0.png&h=28a8c9c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c5c0bdcbf078e3784278536acc69f21428b41d1","tid":2272584,"uid":41458,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T06:50:51.000Z","msg":"香港仲有公義？"},{"pid":"02f505853489be0130db527734fdffc71f6d98c3","tid":2272584,"uid":188306,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T06:51:45.000Z","msg":"殺人放火金腰帶，果然係歷史不斷重演"},{"pid":"04da119eece28374bf28320939cdb206e95db121","tid":2272584,"uid":208165,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T06:51:56.000Z","msg":"屌那